    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small items, often in the form of a disk or resembling a coin, having a religious or devotional subject imprinted, carved, cast, or otherwise marked upon them. They are found in Ancient, Christian, Hindu, and other religious contexts. The tokens may be considered holy in themselves, conferring luck or grace upon those who carry them.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
